{"tid":7317,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"委內瑞拉通脹升級:收款時現金稱重 中產上街拾荒","createTime":"2016-11-27T18:50:53.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T01:42:23.000Z","uid":2110,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e9cda6d75929a5daae09e287ec4a763caf485975","tid":7317,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T18:50:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.aboluowang.com/2016/1127/841924.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.aboluowang.com%2F2016%2F1127%2F841924.html&d=G23sMlIDbip8kPqvS0Sf2MW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=1bbf5e19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.aboluowang.com/2016/1127/841924.html</a><br />\n據英國《每日郵報》11月24日報道，近期，委內瑞拉通脹局勢進一步惡化，政府瘋狂印鈔加速了貨幣貶值的速度，國內超市結賬收款不再是點鈔而是稱重鈔票，中產階級也被迫上街拾荒，形勢十分嚴峻。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，委內瑞拉政府在10月份表示，面額2萬的玻利瓦爾幣不久將投入使用。目前國內使用頻率最高的玻利瓦爾幣面額為100。首都加拉加斯的麵包師布雷默?羅德古斯(Bremmer Rodrigues)無奈地自嘲道：&ldquo;我感覺自己就像毒販子巴勃羅?埃斯科瓦爾，每天錢堆得跟山一樣，越來越多。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n雖然政府一直在矢口否認並拒絕公布經濟數據，但經濟學家預測，如今經濟嚴重依賴石油出口的委內瑞拉的通脹率已達到480%，到2017年則會飆升到1600%，這一數據着實令人乍舌。<br />\n<br />\n隨着經濟危機的加深，該國的軍隊已經介入糧食供應的管理工作。<br />\n<br />\n對此，委內瑞拉總統尼古拉斯?馬杜羅(Nicolas Maduro)寄希望於剛剛與石油輸出國組織(OPEC)簽訂的協議，他在11月23日表示：&ldquo;這一協議刻不容緩，石油出口減少，油價將上漲。我相信我們所做的努力。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cms-bucket.nosdn.127.net/catchpic/d/d2/d21eb7ce8f5032392b8857ccab87fc32.jpg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.nosdn.127.net%2Fcatchpic%2Fd%2Fd2%2Fd21eb7ce8f5032392b8857ccab87fc32.jpg%3FimageView%26thumbnail%3D550x0&h=79cf6ef1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cms-bucket.nosdn.127.net/catchpic/3/37/3741f3427f84899fabe3ca65cc771b57.jpg?imageView&amp;thumbnail=550x0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcms-bucket.nosdn.127.net%2Fcatchpic%2F3%2F37%2F3741f3427f84899fabe3ca65cc771b57.jpg%3FimageView%26thumbnail%3D550x0&h=022b1a82&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03924b649e2c728f3b1d336de58af98c7e6b11bf","tid":7317,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T18:53:32.000Z","msg":"其實係咪應該直接放棄隻貨幣呢"},{"pid":"01bf36cb6f4755677c5799e207a176ae10378e71","tid":7317,"uid":441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T18:55:40.000Z","msg":"真係痴線。幾時變津巴布韋"},{"pid":"a5cabb43eb8eae290b6b956bcbdd3bfb15f5f79f","tid":7317,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T18:56:54.000Z","msg":"去到咁既地步係咪無得救架啦？"},{"pid":"ef7f40311a99c99b645c70ad7526192a2d993e1d","tid":7317,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T19:05:50.000Z","msg":"單一產業收皮就咁樣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d03493649ee9ac584f67d2d1d2380295f54465a3","tid":7317,"uid":4934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T19:41:44.000Z","msg":"第二個津巴布韋"},{"pid":"bde8115eaec88d02d68968e38dcb3891aea5b38a","tid":7317,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T19:51:59.000Z","msg":"香港遲早都一撚樣"},{"pid":"4c81d951578ff5cc0a335fc5fe73dfee2a136f68","tid":7317,"uid":20649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T20:31:42.000Z","msg":"手持午餐肉會點？"},{"pid":"ac43bfde5a83255ab03fc818c160bb7c09f23d91","tid":7317,"uid":13082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T21:06:54.000Z","msg":"浪費紙張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1e0db53a923488d4e78abfd1286cf178d0d47e","tid":7317,"uid":6464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T21:16:27.000Z","msg":"Pablo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36ee3e83ee7377eca2919153c1426e0dac388df","tid":7317,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T23:46:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港遲早都一撚樣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n